WEBVTT

00:01:58.250 --> 00:02:00.768
and otherwise described,

00:02:00.792 --> 00:02:03.893
I am Jomama Jones.

00:02:03.917 --> 00:02:06.768
Some call me a soul sonic superstar,

00:02:06.792 --> 00:02:08.684
and I agree,

00:02:08.708 --> 00:02:12.143
though even in my past
that was from the future.

00:02:12.167 --> 00:02:14.268
Let me take you back to girlhood.

00:02:14.292 --> 00:02:15.851
Picture this:

00:02:15.875 --> 00:02:17.726
it was Planting Day,

00:02:17.750 --> 00:02:19.893
which was a holiday I invented

00:02:19.917 --> 00:02:22.476
for the Black youth
community group I founded.

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:25.601
I dashed home to put on
my gardening ensemble

00:02:25.625 --> 00:02:29.643
when I caught my uncle Freeman red-handed.

00:02:29.667 --> 00:02:34.684
He was standing over my piggy bank
with his hammer raised high.